#: src/routes/_home/-sections/faq.tsx
msgid "Yes, Reactive Resume is available in multiple languages. You can choose your preferred language in the settings page, or using the language switcher in the top right corner. If you don't see your language, or you would like to improve the existing translations, you can <0>contribute to the translations on Crowdin<1> (opens in new tab)</1></0>."
msgstr "Yebo, i-Reactive Resume iyatholakala ngezilimi eziningi. Ungakhetha ulimi olukhethile ekhasini lezilungiselelo, noma usebenzisa isishintshi solimi ekhoneni eliphezulu kwesokudla. Uma ungaboni ulimi lwakho, noma ungathanda ukuthuthukisa ukuhumusha okukhona, ungakwazi <0>ukufaka isandla ekuhumusheni ku-Crowdin<1> (kuvuleka kuthebhu entsha)</1></0>."

#: src/routes/_home/-sections/faq.tsx
msgid "Yes! Reactive Resume is completely free to use, with no hidden costs, premium tiers, or subscription fees. It's open-source and will always remain free."
msgstr "Yebo! I-Reactive Resume imahhala ngokuphelele ukuyisebenzisa, akukho zindleko ezifihliwe, amazinga aphezulu, noma izimali zokubhalisa. Isekelwe umthombo ovulekile futhi izohlala imahhala."

#: src/routes/_home/-sections/features.tsx
msgid "You also have the option to deploy on your own servers using the Docker image."
msgstr "Uphinde ube nenketho yokuyifaka kumaseva akho usebenzisa isithombe se-Docker."

#: src/features/auth/pages/login.tsx
msgid "You can also use your username to login."
msgstr "Ungasebenzisa futhi igama lomsebenzisi wakho ukungena."

#: src/routes/_home/-sections/faq.tsx
msgid "You can share your resume via a unique public URL, protect it with a password, or download it as a PDF to share directly. The choice is yours!"
msgstr "Ungabelana nge-CV yakho nge-URL yomphakathi eyingqayizivele, uyivikele ngephasiwedi, noma uyilande njenge-PDF ukuze wabelane ngqo. Ukukhetha kungokwakho!"

